title: Gromp King Tahm Kench
body:
I think that {{champion:223}} already looks a lot like gromp, so why not give him a gromp skin?

The hat could be a crown or a frog. (or a frog in the crown)

Heres a VERY rough sketch. (NOT what the finished product should look like)

I hope you consider making this skin. (even though the concept art is trash :| )

replies.body: Have you heard of the skin "Rare Pepe Tahm Kench?"
My biggest question is, how do you think Tahm Kench looks like Gromp?
